{
  "texts": [
    "Someone who wants to influence you badly can reach what you speak.",
    "(P.12) I do not know how this data is used, for what purpose, and where it is transmitted other than where I share it.",
    "I don't know if it is abused or not.",
    "I can't comment on either.",
    "(P.12) I feel helpless about the Personal Data Protection Law."
